JALV(1)                                                                         General Commands Manual                                                                        JALV(1)

NNAAMMEE
       jjaallvv -- RRuunn aann LLVV22 pplluuggiinn aass aa JJAACCKK aapppplliiccaattiioonn ((ccoonnssoollee vveerrssiioonn))..

SSYYNNOOPPSSIISS
       jjaallvv [[OOPPTTIIOONN]]...... PPLLUUGGIINN__UURRII

OOPPTTIIOONNSS
       --bb SSIIZZEE
              Buffer size for plugin <=> UI communication.

       --cc SSYYMM==VVAALL
              Set control value (e.g. "vol=1.4").

       --dd     Dump plugin <=> UI communication.

       --UU UURRII Load the UI with the given URI.

       --hh     Print the command line options.

       --ii     Ignore input on stdin (for background use).

       --ll DDIIRR Load state from state directory.

       --nn NNAAMMEE
              Jack client name

       --pp     Print control output changes to stdout.

       --ss     Show plugin UI if possible.

              This option only works when plugins provide a UI that is usable via the non-embeddable showHide interface.  For other, embeddable UIs, use jalv.gtk(1) or jalv.qt(1).

       --tt     Print trace messages from plugin

       --uu UUUUIIDD
              UUID for Jack session restoration.

       --xx     Use only exact Jack client name, and exit if it is taken

CCOOMMMMAANNDDSS
       The Jalv prompt supports several commands for interactive control:

         hheellpp              Display help message
         ccoonnttrroollss          Print settable control values
         mmoonniittoorrss          Print output control values
         pprreesseettss           Print available presets
         pprreesseett UURRII        Set preset
         sseett IINNDDEEXX VVAALLUUEE   Set control value by port index
         sseett SSYYMMBBOOLL VVAALLUUEE  Set control value by symbol
         SSYYMMBBOOLL == VVAALLUUEE    Set control value by symbol

SSEEEE AALLSSOO
       jjaallvv..ggttkk((11)),, jjaallvv..ggttkkmmmm((11)),, jjaallvv..qqtt((22)),, llvv22llss((11)),, jjaacckkdd((11))

AAUUTTHHOORR
